metadata.name: Queen Of The Deep by BooMan
metadata.description: The Deep Sea is as dangerous as it is beautiful. I have always had a fascination with underwater creatures and have always thought that there was an argument for the deep sea being as limitless as outer space. Queen of the deep is the protector of the deep sea and watches over its creatures. Created with an AI generated base and brought to life with hand drawing, color enhancements and motion graphics. Mesmerizing!
